p.d: One. Of. The. Best. Fucks. Of. My. Life. It was never to be. We'd set up three or four shoots with Miss Trixx already only to have them all fall through. Jinxed, we reckoned. But then I bumped into her at a party and there was real chemistry so we set another date and bingo, her, me and Andy all found ourselves in the same room finally, in her flat in Birmingham.
